        "ggshYHIIH0L_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">New Customers Only</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Code: <strong>$10Off-LBORA</strong></span></p>",
        "gg3ObLN5Y8r_defaultLabel": "Copy",
        "ggKhefd8AVd_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Over $200</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Code: <strong>$25Off-LBORA</strong></span></p>",
        "ggocj0KQQUr_defaultLabel": "Copy",
        "ggm0hC2a59f_text": "Quantity",
        "ggM3a8aHiru_text": "<p><u>Size Guide</u></p>",
        "ggujDb1-A41_text": "<p><a href=\"https://shoplbora.com/pages/process-flow\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Process Flow</u></a></p>",
        "ggUK2hIvqMO_label": "Add To cart",
        "ggUK2hIvqMO_outOfStockLabel": "Out of stock",
        "ggUK2hIvqMO_unavailableLabel": "Unavailable",
        "ggIvNIugowr_label": "Buy Now",
        "ggIvNIugowr_outOfStockLabel": "Out of stock",
        "ggIvNIugowr_unavailableLabel": "Unavailable",
        "ggL85oxCgCt_childItem_0": "<p>Discription</p>",
        "ggL85oxCgCt_childItem_1": "<p>Size+fit</p>",
        "ggL85oxCgCt_childItem_2": "<p>Free Shipping</p>",
        "ggWccoCWPlH_viewMoreText": "Show more",
        "ggWccoCWPlH_viewLessText": "Show less",
        "ggagGj567_n_text": "<p>At <span style=\"color:#3B3B3B;\">Lbora</span>, our hats are crafted with precision to ensure a tailored and flattering fit.</p><p> </p><p><strong>True to Size:</strong><br>Each style is designed to fit true to size, following standard international headwear measurements. Simply select your usual hat size for the most comfortable fit.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Between Sizes:</strong><br>If you find yourself between sizes, we recommend using one of our premium hat fillers. Designed for subtle comfort, they provide a secure fit without compromising the hat’s shape or style.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Need Assistance</strong>:<br>Not sure of your size? Visit our <a href=\"https://luxebrims.com/pages/hat-size-guide\"><u>Hat Size Guide</u></a> or reach out to our support team — we're here to help you find your perfect fit.</p>",
        "ggRa1qdeaB__text": "<p><span style=\"color:#3B3B3B;\">Lbora delivers to customers around the world — with free shipping and estimated delivery in 20-25 business days.</span><br><span style=\"color:#3B3B3B;\">Note: Delivery times may vary slightly depending on your location.</span></p>",
        "ggODL_QU1nu_childItem_0": "<p>Security and Service</p>",
        "ggoBqigMSJW_text": "<p>Payment Security</p>",
        "ggA-bjY31sD_text": "<p>Your payment security matters to us. Lbora partners exclusively with certified payment service providers who are committed to protecting and maintaining the confidentiality of your payment information.</p>",
        "ggSjQVgOFCb_text": "<p>Privacy Protection  </p>",
        "ggGHGvQgckX_text": "<p>At Lbora, we protect your privacy with industry-standard encryption. Your shipping address, payment information, and purchase details are secured throughout your entire shopping experience. Shop with confidence.</p>",
        "ggUWHchKLTN_text": "<p>Efficient and Safe Logitics</p>",
        "ggdwBSWcPdo_text": "<p>At Lbora, we deliver with security and efficiency. Track your order in real-time, and protect your purchase with our optional Shipping Protection—covering delays, damage, or loss during transit.<a href=\"https://www.shipsurance.com/surecircle/terms\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#3393CC;\"><strong><u>learn more</u></strong></span></a></p>",
        "gg1elQw0vld_text": "<p>Customer Service</p>",
        "ggrjBheTtwl_text": "<p>We're here to help. If you encounter any problems during or after shopping, Lbora's customer service team is ready to assist you.</p>",
        "gg-Vwvq42Vj_text": "Payment Security",
        "ggk9tSva9R-_text": "Privacy Protection",
        "gg0062YpiqU_text": "Efficient and Safe Logitics",
        "ggTTJpRkYts_text": "Customer Service"
      }
